ch mainly allocate capital to thirdparty portfolio managers bsa portfolio managers the bsa portfolio managers may invest and trade on margin or otherwise in debt and equity securities and other financial instruments including derivatives the bsa portfolio managers generally will manage capital exclusively for the bsa funds during an initial investment period although they may manage capital for bsa affiliates during such exclusivity period thereafter the bsa portfolio managers may invest capital for other investors through a hedge fund andor managed account platform bsa also directly manages and trades a portion of the bsa master fund’s assets in a subaccount of the bsa master fund the center book and uses a hedge account designed to achieve a marketneutral profile in aggregate for the bsa funds in their management of the center book bsa invests and trades on margin or otherwise directly in debt and equity securities and other financial instruments including derivativesbsa allocates the bsa funds’ capital to bsa portfolio managers that pursue a range of investment strategies and invest in various securities and financial instruments the firm seeks to take advantage of investment opportunities across asset classes and sectors bsa’s primary goal is to identify the right talent pool of bsa portfolio managers without specific diversification requirements or limitations chairman  chief executive officer prior   pjt partners inc pjt partners inc engages in the provision of strategic advisory restructuring and reorganization and funds advisory services to corporations financial sponsors institutional investors and governments it also involves in fund placement and secondary advisory services for alternative investment managers the company was founded in october  and is headquartered in new york ny professional   prior blackstone mezzanine advisors ii lp see  more listings with relsci professional start my free trial ➤ see  more boards  committees corporate boards ▾ chairma