 stern dean of the yale school of architecture in january  schwarzman was on the cover of the shanghai business review to share his vision about the chinese economy against the backdrop of his scholarship the story was supported by kevin rudd former prime minister of australia and on the international advisory board of schwarzman scholars president trumps strategic and policy forumedit main article strategic and policy forum in late  schwarzman helped put together a team of corporate executives to advise president donald trump on jobs and the economy the group includes jpmorgan chase jpm ceo jamie dimon walt disney dis boss bob iger and former ge leader jack welch in february schwarzman was named as chair of the member presidents strategic and policy forum which brings together ceos of americas biggest corporations banks and investment firms to consult with the president on how to create jobs and improve growth for the us economy infrastructure funds blackstone and saudi arabiaedit increasingly large investors such as blackstone are investing in infrastructure such as airports public works and railways blackstone with  billion in assets is expanding into infrastructure investments the blackstone group joined forces with saudi arabia in may  establishing a  billion infrastructure fund to invest in stateside infrastructure projects saudi arabia will provide  of the fund which could lead to  billion in total infrastructure investments on a leveraged basis referencesedit  stephen schwarzman blackstones  billion man forbes retrieved november     stephen schwarzman forbescom retrieved december     a b c nocera joe february   steve schwarzman explains why he counsels trump retrieved march   – via wwwbloombergcom   live from new york it’s steve schwarzman the new york times retrieved december     the worlds  richest jews   jewish world  jerusalem post jpostcom retrieved december     a b weddings  christine hearst s a schwarzman nytimescom november   retrieved december     p